Class AbstractMark

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ausregistry.jtoolkit2.se.tmch.AbstractMark
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CourtValidatedMark, Trademark, TreatyOrStatute

    public abstract class AbstractMark
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an abstract mark from the Trademark Clearing House extension, represented by the "abstractMark" element of type "abstractMarkType" in the "urn:ietf:params:xml:ns:mark-1.0" namespace, defined in the "mark-1.0.xsd" schema.
